WEBVTT

00:03.851 --> 00:05.477
Hi! I'm the bus driver.

00:05.653 --> 00:10.808
Listen, I've got to leave for a little while, so can you watch things for me until I get back?

00:11.231 --> 00:13.175
Thanks. Oh, and remember:...

00:14.486 --> 00:17.145
...don't let the pigeon drive the bus!

00:24.423 --> 00:25.826
I thought he'd never leave.

00:29.373 --> 00:30.784
Hey, can I drive the bus?

00:32.093 --> 00:35.117
Please? I'll be careful.

00:38.135 --> 00:40.447
I tell you what: I'll just steer.

00:41.737 --> 00:44.523
My cousin Herb drives a bus almost every day!

00:45.297 --> 00:46.183
True story.

00:51.826 --> 00:52.871
Pigeon at the wheel!

00:54.203 --> 00:57.389
No? I never get to do anything!

00:58.619 --> 01:00.155
Hey, I've got an idea.

01:00.498 --> 01:01.743
Let's play "Drive the Bus"!

01:02.895 --> 01:04.047
I'll go first!

01:07.450 --> 01:09.355
C'mon! Just once around the block!

01:10.669 --> 01:12.030
I'll be your best friend!

01:13.037 --> 01:14.699
How about I give you five bucks?

01:15.818 --> 01:16.582
No fair!

01:17.671 --> 01:19.226
I bet your mom would let me.

01:20.227 --> 01:21.235
What's the big deal?

01:22.343 --> 01:23.442
I have dreams, you know!

01:24.451 --> 01:25.040
Fine.

01:26.001 --> 01:27.861
Let me drive the bus!

01:40.431 --> 01:41.253
I'm back!

01:41.741 --> 01:44.134
You didn't let the pigeon drive the bus, did you?

01:45.353 --> 01:46.703
Great.  Thanks a lot.

01:55.561 --> 01:56.268
Bye!

